import TNLean.MPS.BNT.PermutationRigidity.Matching

/-!
# Permutation rigidity for basis-of-normal-tensors (BNT) decompositions

This module collects the paper-hypothesis permutation-rigidity theorem for
BNT decompositions.  Starting from proportional full MPV families and explicit
decompositions into asymptotically orthonormal BNT blocks, the theorem produces
a permutation of blocks, equality of bond dimensions, and gauge-phase
equivalence for each corresponding block.
-/
